	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Turns out the problem was, I had entered ".asm" instead of just "asm". When I changed it to "asm" my user defined lang overrode the default one. How refreshing to finally be able to open all my source files at once and not have to select my lang for each one I want to look at.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /> I can't believe I put up with that for so long.

		

		</td>
