<br />
<br />For now I'm using Notepad++ but if my prototype for my ca65 text editor goes well, I may use it less for 6502 coding.  The current concept is to allow syntax highlighting, pull down with name of symbols/function for finding them, suggestion for name based on the symbols defined in your code etc.
<br />
<br />If it become more than a prototype, I may post it someday. For now I can only work only a few minutes per day during lunch time so I'm not expecting anything for a while.  I have a few other ideas but unless I can make them work, I won't mention them yet.

		

